          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Gas cells filled with natural krypton to a pressure",
                "of 1-2 bar absolute."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "EXTB",
                "STTA",
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Natural krypton was irradiated in stacked gas cells",
                "windowed 15 micron kapton. Primary deuteron energies",
                "were 14.2 9.9, 9.7 and 7.4 MeV.",
                "Beam current 0.1 microamp. Ti and Fe monitors were used",
                "21 and 12 micron thick respectivelly.",
                "Charge integrated by Faraday-Cup.  Nuclear",
                "data were taken from E.Brwne and R.B.Firestone Table",
                "of Radioactive Isotopes Ed.V.S.Shirley, Wiley 1986.",
                "The mean energy in the monitor foils and in the gas",
                "cells were calculated using tables of H.H.Andersen,",
                "J.F.Ziegler,Hydrogen Stopping Powers and Ranges in All",
                "Elements, Vol.3,Pergamon Press, New York, 1977."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "EN-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                "The Error of the energy was calculated taking",
                "into account the initial uncertainty the sraggling of",
                "the beam and the errors in the thickness of the targets",
                "The estimated energy scale error was +-0.3 MeV at the",
                "first cell and +-0.7 MeV at the last cell in the stack."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The error of the cross section data were",
                "estimated by summing up the squares of the individual",
                "relative errors and taking the square root of it.",
                "Detector efficiency was  5%. The overall uncertainty",
                "reached  13%."
              ]
            }
          ],
